 />\n出行：不宜<br />\n<br />\n姻緣：靜觀其變<br />\n<br />\n行人：未動身<br />\n<br />\n生育：恐有危險<br />\n<br />\n訴訟：要忍耐<br />\n<br />\n事業：忌家人合夥<br />\n<br />\n搬遷：不宜<br />\n<br />\n自身：需修心行善<br />\n<br />\n疾病：小心有急危<br />\n<br />\n財運：不佳"},{"pid":"fc35e50a20bb64f3ad63f259539a9a0bcf25760a","tid":1981872,"uid":57221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44d7bc68329f1991505ffbae1f0dc7a9eac24ead","tid":1981872,"uid":37722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ba4402adf5669f0f9abac122e57d00e3c49e18e","tid":1981872,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"167c1a276d9a14ea170c578d239f8dc31981d309","tid":1981872,"uid":55056,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:18:33.000Z","msg":"問佢權責係邊條法例到寫明"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:19:44.000Z","msg":"無記者問？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:28:41.000Z","msg":"淨聽左頭3個記者問題，第一同第三個記者廢嘅，係得第二個先到肉少少，但係都係無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:29:43.000Z","msg":"依家淨係俾垃圾記者入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有料全部唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47564a84ab2422e5654645f5d886de6d5a87d36","tid":1981872,"uid":191667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:30:14.000Z","msg":"搞唔掂23條依家唸住打茅波搬龍門"},{"pid":"9664f91830ed1b789e68b640eaf40e5c58373a23","tid":1981872,"uid":220359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:30:38.000Z","msg":"真係笑話，自降香港地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182d36a04ac01adc9546c4d45fea3589ce303211","tid":1981872,"uid":9577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44d7bc68329f1991505ffbae1f0dc7a9eac24ead","tid":1981872,"uid":37722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ba4402adf5669f0f9abac122e57d00e3c49e18e","tid":1981872,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"167c1a276d9a14ea170c578d239f8dc31981d309