0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:29:26.000Z","msg":"諗起當年車公27簽<br />\n<br />\n車公靈簽 第二十七簽：下籤<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">簽文：君不須防人不肖，眼前鬼卒皆為妖；秦王徒把長城築，福去禍來因自招。</span><br />\n<br />\n解簽：<span style=\"color: red;\">內有家鬼，自身不安</span>，家宅不吉，求財不遂<br />\n<br />\n斷簽：家宅有鬼，占病兇險，自身作孽，出入撞鬼，婚姻大凶，求財虧本，暴虐不仁，自作妖孽，時運極滯，非改不可<br />\n<br />\n家宅：不吉，慎防家人<br />\n<br />\n出行：不宜<br />\n<br />\n姻緣：靜觀其變<br />\n<br />\n行人：未動身<br />\n<br />\n生育：恐有危險<br />\n<br />\n訴訟：要忍耐<br />\n<br />\n事業：忌家人合夥<br />\n<br />\n搬遷：不宜<br />\n<br />\n自身：需修心行善<br />\n<br />\n疾病：小心有急危<br />\n<br />\n財運：不佳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"見你咁講，我就去d算命網求支車公廟簽，屌你老母，有真係俾我求到呢支簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nwDKXTd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnwDKXTd.png&h=bf327610&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fb46e459d2ee681ddaf2b61b65b7a6fa14c4232","tid":1981872,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:54:39.000Z","msg":"基本法有咁講？"},{"pid":"2741d7960511bd9fdd3757027e2dbc90b13bdf9f","tid":1981872,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43627daca09447a7bd636559f269e0a31caaaee9","tid":1981872,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:57:57.000Z","msg":"一國一制"},{"pid":"6707367e69f3be44bb518341e988f90980cea1cc","tid":1981872,"uid":221343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"50年未到一半就徹底玩完"},{"pid":"ad87a31ba0fa4544353d8eeae70bde6770351305","tid":1981